ed the island's ongoing energy crisis. Ageing infrastructure and fuel shortages have caused frequent power outages for months. US sanctions are blamed by the government for limiting fuel imports. The situation has worsened amid a prolonged economic crisis on the island.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/cubas-national-grid-completely-collapses-nearly-10-million-in-darkness/articleshow/132221808.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/cubas-national-grid-completely-collapses-nearly-10-million-in-darkness/articleshow/132221808.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-06T22:33:33+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132221902,imgsize-601517.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA['Closer than people realise': Trump says both Putin, Zelenskyy want war to end]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132221201.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/closer-than-people-realise-trump-says-both-putin-zelenskyy-want-war-to-end/articleshow/132221201.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/closer-than-people-realise-trump-says-both-putin-zelenskyy-want-war-to-end/articleshow/132221201.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-06T22:14:01+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132221494,imgsize-67194.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Scientists have found 99.7% chance of life in this planet and no, it's not Mars]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132221149.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Scientists detected gases on exoplanet K2-18b linked to life on Earth.  The James Webb Space Telescope's future results show a tentative signal of dimethyl sulfide.  This discovery is not yet confirmed and requires further observation for verification.  K2-18b orbits its star in the habitable zone, making it a prime candidate.  Future observations will determine if this represents a historic breakthrough in astrobiology.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/scientists-have-found-99-7-chance-of-life-in-this-planet-and-no-its-not-mars/articleshow/132221149.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/scientists-have-found-99-7-chance-of-life-in-this-planet-and-no-its-not-mars/articleshow/132221149.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-06T22:03:12+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI Science Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132221221,imgsize-172587.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[300,000-year-old Homo naledi fossils from a South African cave suggest the ancient human relative may have been a female-only species, new study reveals]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132220531.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[A recent examination of ancient dental remains from South Africa's cave systems has led to a striking conclusion. Proteomic analysis revealed solely female protein markers in the samples examined. This intriguing finding implies that all identified Homo naledi individuals could potentially be female. Researchers are currently delving into possible explanations for this unexpected trend, which raises significant questions regarding established beliefs about the species' gender distribution.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/300000-year-old-homo-naledi-fossils-from-a-south-african-cave-suggest-the-ancient-human-relative-may-have-been-a-female-only-species-new-study-reveals/articleshow/132220531.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/science/300000-year-old-homo-naledi-fossils-from-a-south-african-cave-suggest-the-ancient-human-relative-may-have-been-a-female-only-species-new-study-reveals/articleshow/132220531.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-06T21:47:13+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI Science Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-132221019,imgsize-149532.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[“I don’t fear these…”: Candace Owens reignites Erika Kirk feud during Tyler Robinson hearing in Charlie Kirk case]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/132220670.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Candace Owens reacted strongly as Tyler Robinson’s preliminary hearing began on July 6. She called the proceedings a “show trial,” questioned how evidence is being handled and criticized the court process. In a second post, she shared a faith-based message dedicated to Charlie Kirk. The hearing will determine whether prosecutors have enough evidence to move the case to trial.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/i-dont-fear-these-candace-owens-reignites-erika-kirk-feud-during-tyler-robinson-hearing-in-charlie-kirk-case/articleshow/132220670.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/i-dont-fear-these-candace-owens-reignites-erika-kirk-feud-during-tyler-robinson-hearing-in-charlie-kirk-case/articleshow/132220670.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-07-06T21:19:46+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Sumit Roy</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-13222